413
00:30:31.041 --> 00:30:32.625
<i>We analysed the night traffic</i>
<i>on that route.</i>

414
00:30:32.708 --> 00:30:34.958
So. by the time he reached home.

415
00:30:35.041 --> 00:30:36.541
