427
00:31:06.958 --> 00:31:09.083
<i>Ma'am. she's in a medically induced coma.</i>

428
00:31:10.625 --> 00:31:12.375
<i>She was attacked directly on her neck.</i>

429
00:31:13.041 --> 00:31:15.208
